-- Fund Manager Value Partners Appoints Chan Sheung Lai as CEO, Board Member
-- Joshua Fellman
-- 2010-06-23T09:37:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/fund-manager-value-partners-appoints-chan-sheung-lai-as-ceo-board-member.html

          
          
             Value Partners Group Ltd. has
appointed Chan Sheung Lai as chief executive officer and an
executive director at an annual salary of HK$1.95 million plus
bonus, it said in a Hong Kong stock exchange filing today.  
 The fund manager also said it promoted Louis So to co-chief
investment officer and Tse Wai Ming to deputy chief executive
officer. Chairman Cheah Cheng Hye has been redesignated co-chief
investment officer from chief investment officer.  
          
          


  


        